snippet.title: Flooded - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Flooded on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1795470/Flooded

Optimize your production on an island which shrinks over time. In this fresh take on the RTS genre you need to gather enough resources to flee to safety, while the surrounding world is getting flooded.

#Flooded #trailer #indiegames
